2. http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/03/12/bp-oil-spill-gulf-of-mexico-oil-lobbyists_n_1335556.html

3. http://gtpac.org/2010/07/boeing-submits-its-8000-page-tanker-bid-to-af/


